      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GOLD ALASKA (7) is worth forgiving for her last effort when seventh (26.18) at this track over 457m. Solid record here including two wins. Has ability and looks hard to stop. KONSTANTIN (4) continues to race well but is struggling to break through, placing at his last five runs. Last time finished 2nd in a Grade 5 on April 1 over 350m at Q Straight behind Special Rocky beaten 5 lengths (19.16). Racing well and deserves a win. TARAWI BUSTER (1) has been hard to follow lately, running sixth (25.73) last time but prior to that ran very well when placed at this track. Can hit the frame this time. SEAWAY CRUISER (2) was out of the money here last time out but can bounce back.",
